Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.80,0:00:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.00,0:00:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贏了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.84,0:00:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要舉行慶功派對耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.30,0:00:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舉行派對，不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.15,0:00:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.42,0:00:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們好，各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.19,0:00:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們不准動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.69,0:00:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好兇哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.49,0:00:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要行使\N基爾特公會的登艦特權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.56,0:00:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本艦和基爾特公會\N正處於交戰狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.20,0:00:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們只能算是俘虜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.24,0:00:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.57,0:00:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好別惹帶著小羊的母羊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.71,0:00:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前還是低調處理吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.24,0:00:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔，魯修拉他很厲害的唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.95,0:01:03.35,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,just keep on trying, keep on flying\N{\c&HFFBF00&}just keep on trying, keep on flying
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.42,0:01:06.48,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the light\N{\c&HFFBF00&}I will be the light
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.03,0:01:13.76,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說把黎明　當作是一個開始\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜明けをひと　つの始まりとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.37,0:01:20.97,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說現在就是來臨的時刻\N{\c&HFFBF00&}今が来るべき時だとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.28,0:01:27.58,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,與你的煙雲時代交響曲 飛向雲海的彼端 \N{\c&HFFBF00&}君とのCloud Age Symphony  雲の海の向こうに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.65,0:01:35.68,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,飛往光芒照射的方向\N{\c&HFFBF00&}光が射す方へ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.86,0:01:50.17,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah～是否可以遇見有如魔法的那瞬間？\N{\c&HFFBF00&}Ah～魔法のような一瞬に会えるのか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.24,0:02:04.55,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,取代寒冷的黑夜  我倆展翅飛翔\N{\c&HFFBF00&}冷たい夜を引き替えに  二人は羽ばたいて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.62,0:02:14.79,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,在那盡頭  抓住了永恆…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}永远を掴む、その果てには
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.84,0:02:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8dccf0&}各就各位\NDevelop
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.73,0:02:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.53,0:02:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.90,0:02:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.07,0:02:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葛溫他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.41,0:03:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這兒可真熱鬧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.24,0:03:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.54,0:03:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他們拿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.71,0:03:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的，魯修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.02,0:03:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我安靜一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.12,0:03:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葛溫你還好吧\N振作點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.82,0:03:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，他昏過去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.22,0:03:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.36,0:03:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，魯修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.80,0:03:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.10,0:03:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是俘虜對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.60,0:03:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下，把貨物帶回帝都\N會不會太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.34,0:03:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是早就說過了嗎\N那個人是不值得信任的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.98,0:03:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他明明在拍賣會裡\N把關鍵謎詩弄到了手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.08,0:03:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼卻不來報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.85,0:03:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下已經說過EXILE一事\N要全權交給公主殿下處理了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.79,0:03:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我女兒她有造反的嫌疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.46,0:03:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.66,0:03:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把貨物移到烏爾班號上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.56,0:03:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.36,0:03:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.90,0:03:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.89,0:04:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在記憶的彼方存在的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.56,0:04:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奧妙的詩句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.77,0:04:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安那托勒皇帝有什麼動靜沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.23,0:04:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從王宮派出一架先鋒艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.24,0:04:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目的地呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.01,0:04:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是正在諾齊亞的艦隊那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.51,0:04:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問該如何處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.51,0:04:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨他們去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.79,0:05:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧他人在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.93,0:05:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尚未收到報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.93,0:05:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真拿這孩子沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.54,0:05:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這房間不錯嘛，有夠髒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.51,0:05:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.04,0:05:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧‧艾拉克萊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.31,0:05:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是戴芬妮總帥的族人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.91,0:05:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問基爾特的名門子弟\N來這裡有何貴幹嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.92,0:05:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是來見英麥曼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.05,0:05:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.15,0:05:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他那迴轉有多漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.29,0:05:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是衝著艾兒‧薇絲來的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.99,0:05:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒興趣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.03,0:05:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不是艦長先生你的寶貝嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.70,0:05:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不相信我是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.93,0:05:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼為了表示友好\N讓我給你一份見面禮好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.27,0:05:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可別告訴戴芬妮哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.24,0:05:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在天空的彼方存在的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.55,0:05:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.65,0:05:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.35,0:06:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是艾拉克萊家\N代代相傳的關鍵謎詩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.66,0:06:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漢彌爾敦，達格貝，巴席安努
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.99,0:06:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關鍵謎詩雖然也傳給了\N基爾特的另外三個家族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.86,0:06:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他們都已遭到了整肅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.60,0:06:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思說總帥她\N四句都已經知道了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.17,0:06:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴芬妮她只知道一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.31,0:06:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何況拍賣會上\N她又輸給了艦長先生你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.87,0:06:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長先生你知道幾句啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.08,0:06:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩句嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.68,0:06:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了，是三句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.65,0:06:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.98,0:06:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正跟我沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.82,0:06:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，我可以去找英麥曼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.10,0:06:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再搭乘\N戰鬥用的先鋒艇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.34,0:06:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士你和我所看的天空\N彼此已經不一樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.88,0:06:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我暸解克勞士\N你想投入戰鬥的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.01,0:07:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也曾經試著要去努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.18,0:07:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但畢竟還是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.79,0:07:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.55,0:07:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說你用來戰鬥的先鋒艇\N就讓我來負責照顧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.72,0:07:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要成為克勞士你的機械師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.36,0:07:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士你去照顧五號機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.40,0:07:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽著，我一定會把\N爸爸他們的先鋒艇修好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.60,0:07:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以克勞士你也別忘了\N飛越大風暴區的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.11,0:07:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要好好加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.31,0:07:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦，打起精神來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.01,0:07:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是要保護艾兒和我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.42,0:07:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴你一個好消息哦，英麥曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.12,0:07:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天哪，來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.35,0:07:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你聽我說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.46,0:07:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長先生他任命你來\N負責監視我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.96,0:07:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.73,0:07:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.03,0:07:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不對，魯修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.20,0:07:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以從現在開始\N你要一直和我在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.80,0:08:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比賽裡最後一次進維修站時\N只補給一半的燃料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.21,0:08:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是妳的主意嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.91,0:08:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.11,0:08:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是個不錯的主意哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.71,0:08:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我等於是輸在妳手下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.31,0:08:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你聽到沒，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.98,0:08:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，英麥曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.48,0:08:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你看看艦載機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.05,0:08:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了，我自己來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.09,0:08:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從上次空戰裡的印象來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.56,0:08:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這機體的平衡性太差了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.56,0:08:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它的飛行阻力也有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.89,0:08:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到他人挺好的嘛\N而且右邊的轉矩.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.94,0:08:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信號彈確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.47,0:08:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是烏爾班號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.61,0:08:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦橋下令，確保通訊筒暢通\N值班機出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.68,0:08:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再重複一遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.48,0:08:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確保通訊筒暢通，值班機出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.75,0:08:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗絲，太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.30,0:09:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這構造還真是原始啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.40,0:09:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.34,0:09:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣掉下去不就死定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.17,0:09:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯修拉，你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.51,0:09:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是用焊鉛來固定的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.04,0:09:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.71,0:09:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀之戰艦的驅動系統\N是怎樣的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.92,0:09:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我哪曉得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.18,0:09:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擁有沒有登記在基爾特公會下\N組件的神祕船艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.12,0:09:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得很令人好奇嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.66,0:09:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，帶我去輪機室好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.39,0:09:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然不可以，再說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.80,0:09:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就放任那兩個人不管嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.74,0:09:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們至少可以讓\N基爾特投鼠忌器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.68,0:09:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們似乎對克勞地亞組件\N很感興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.55,0:09:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨他們去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.18,0:09:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想讓他們見見輪機長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.25,0:09:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說雷修斯嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.52,0:09:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.09,0:10:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜‧魏斯洛\N回來跟您報到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.20,0:10:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是烏爾班號給您的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.20,0:10:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.94,0:10:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恕我告退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.62,0:10:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她還是那麼硬邦邦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.79,0:10:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家已經很盡力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.49,0:10:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文生他希望和我見個面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.06,0:10:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝終於要有所行動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.53,0:10:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大型貨櫃準備起飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.37,0:10:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七分鐘後出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.67,0:10:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再重複一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.50,0:10:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大型貨櫃準備起飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.80,0:10:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注入燃料\N七分鐘後出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.24,0:10:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要慢吞吞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.24,0:10:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快把後備的燃料箱拿來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.91,0:10:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫那邊的先鋒艇移開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.48,0:10:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.65,0:10:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你來擔任護航
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.39,0:11:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.12,0:11:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.72,0:11:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士他的經驗不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.93,0:11:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,選他擔任護航的駕駛員\N我不認為是適當的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.76,0:11:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜，這是艦長的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.53,0:11:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是克勞士他沒有領航員…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.00,0:11:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.80,0:11:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗絲…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.04,0:11:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來當克勞士的領航員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.84,0:11:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.01,0:11:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我准許
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.08,0:11:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.99,0:11:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.19,0:11:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的天空裡已經沒有了自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.76,0:11:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照囉，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.73,0:11:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.96,0:11:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了，快點準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.85,0:13:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，亞力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.19,0:13:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.96,0:13:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自從奧特朗會戰以來\N就沒看到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.63,0:13:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基爾特，格拉艾斯號，賈卡羅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.20,0:13:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凡是你所到之處\N果然是寸草不生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.87,0:13:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到你還是一樣不苟言笑\N真是令人開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.44,0:13:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有事快說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.92,0:13:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總不好意思空著手來跟你見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.62,0:13:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我帶了好東西來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.45,0:13:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是烏爾班號上的名產\N軍艦咖啡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.59,0:13:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你拿去嚐嚐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.80,0:14:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問一下，艾麗絲蒂亞小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.00,0:14:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我艾麗絲就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.80,0:14:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問妳在看什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.97,0:14:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星星…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.01,0:14:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星星變得不可靠起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.22,0:14:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算觀察星象\N也判斷不出正確的方位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.52,0:14:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這片天空裡正在發生著什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.73,0:14:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,味道很香吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.63,0:14:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是北部高地的\N極品咖啡豆呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.02,0:14:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,煮好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.66,0:15:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼比在寒夜裡\N來一杯這玩意更好的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.34,0:15:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝陛下他很擔心貨物的狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.97,0:15:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聖旨上寫著要我問出關鍵謎詩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.14,0:15:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並要我把貨物帶回帝都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.88,0:15:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思是叫我來進行回收
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.68,0:15:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.09,0:15:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我光是對付諾齊亞那邊的\N度西斯艦隊就已經忙不過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.82,0:15:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真會給人找麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.20,0:15:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,內容到底是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.83,0:15:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能把貨物交給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.74,0:15:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.44,0:15:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你這麼做代表什麼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.95,0:15:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正是這個打算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.55,0:15:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.99,0:16:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就不得不和你交戰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.33,0:16:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會很不好過哦，亞力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.32,0:16:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.62,0:16:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.87,0:16:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.51,0:16:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烏爾班號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.34,0:17:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最好是看清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.70,0:17:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼看這都是基爾特的組件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.54,0:17:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是取自沈沒的船艦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.24,0:17:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請您小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.64,0:17:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許還有叛國殘黨躲在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.48,0:17:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有魯修拉在\N就沒什麼好怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.25,0:17:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在這裡做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.78,0:17:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們是…基爾特公會的人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.22,0:17:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老爺爺你也是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.32,0:17:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫迪奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.56,0:17:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是滿手血腥的\N艾拉克萊家的毛頭小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.93,0:17:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也長大了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.80,0:17:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，沒想到你居然認識我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.57,0:17:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老爺爺你為什麼在這裡呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.21,0:18:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡很久了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.81,0:18:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別妨礙我工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.81,0:18:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時和你一起離開基爾特的\N那些人都怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.82,0:18:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去的事我早就忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.85,0:18:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是氣象控制裝置的異常\N後來是怎樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.92,0:18:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果放著不管的話\N世界會完蛋哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.76,0:18:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.49,0:18:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們沒告訴你嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.66,0:18:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.63,0:18:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來基爾特公會\N是打算放棄度西斯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.33,0:18:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老爺爺你也下西洋棋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.97,0:18:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很強唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.14,0:18:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會再來玩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.74,0:18:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧，魯修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.98,0:18:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.55,0:18:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次要比個高下哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.19,0:19:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天就快亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.46,0:19:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.96,0:19:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.86,0:19:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你那麼奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.06,0:19:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.17,0:19:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還把克勞士叫成英麥曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.50,0:19:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英麥曼就是英麥曼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.11,0:19:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士就是克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.28,0:19:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而妳呢，則是艾兒‧薇絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.25,0:19:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.18,0:19:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的事情可多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.45,0:19:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來讀詩給妳聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.15,0:19:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.93,0:20:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞力克斯，我有話跟你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.60,0:20:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.90,0:20:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烏爾班號來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.31,0:20:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼詩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.45,0:20:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在天空的彼方存在的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.99,0:21:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳果然是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.36,0:21:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦，妳已經起來了啊，艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.90,0:21:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒，發生什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.80,0:21:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你對艾兒做了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.40,0:21:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是讀了詩給她聽而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.50,0:21:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.70,0:21:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.14,0:21:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.22,0:21:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞地亞壓持續上升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.15,0:21:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原因呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.02,0:21:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.32,0:21:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高度正在上升中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.92,0:21:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太奇怪了，氣壓正在急速下降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.76,0:21:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦內蒸汽壓上升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.16,0:21:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停機庫發生火災
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.03,0:21:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,輪機室，把克勞地亞壓降到50%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.13,0:21:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞地亞管進行繞流處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.51,0:21:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是烏爾班號的關係嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.44,0:21:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.72,0:22:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厲害，太厲害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.66,0:22:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.22,0:22:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指引迷路的孩子\N回到母親手中的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.13,0:22:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.32,0:22:40.65,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,黑夜的時光逐漸逼近\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜の時間が迫り来る
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.22,0:22:47.28,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你離我如此接近感覺  卻好遠…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたはこんな近く でも遠い…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.36,0:22:52.46,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你的憧憬是什麼\N{\c&HFFBF00&}何に憧れて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.53,0:22:58.47,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,心中想的又是誰\N{\c&HFFBF00&}だれを想うのか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.54,0:23:04.07,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你奮不顧身的身影\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いのち賭ける姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.14,0:23:12.92,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,有一種透明的美麗  令我噤聲無言\N{\c&HFFBF00&}透き通る美しさに 言葉を飲んだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.99,0:23:18.95,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你欲飛往天際\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたが空を行くなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.02,0:23:24.59,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我願成為你的翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}わたしは翼になりたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.66,0:23:30.43,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,無論風有多麼強\N{\c&HFFBF00&}どんなに強い風にも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.50,0:23:36.31,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,也永遠不會折斷的柔婉翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}けして折れない しなやかな羽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.38,0:23:48.95,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,相信有一天  我會擁有那樣一對翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いつか　きっと持つから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.69,0:23:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(下回預告)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.46,0:23:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前進方向，龍之牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.26,0:23:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迎擊烏爾班號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.23,0:23:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活捉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.80,0:24:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有擊沈它的氣魄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.60,0:24:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是打不贏亞力克斯的\N銀之戰艦的
